  m_Text: "\u2022  Fill the grid so every cell holds a sun or a moon.\n\u2022  Each
    row (and column) has equal suns and moons, with at most 2 identical symbols adjacent.\n\u2022 
    Cells split by = must match; cells split by \xD7 must differ."
